full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/20/2023 CERTIFICATE OF MATRIMONY THE UNDERSIGNED, PARISH PRIEST OF THE PARISH OF SAN PEDRO SULA APOSTLE CATHEDRAL, OF THE BISHOPRIC OF SAN PEDRO SULA. CERTIFIES: THAT IN THE REGISTRY OF MATRIMONY NO. T-B-9 AND ON PAGE # 164 THERE IS A CERTIFICATE THAT SAYS: ON THE 17th OF October 19 59 IN San Pedro Sula PARISH OF Catedral / THE REV. P. Eduaro Rodriguez PREVIOUS INFORMATION AND REQUIRED THE MUTUAL CONSENT OF WORDS BY THE PRESENT, JOINED IN MATRIMONY Maniuel De Jesus Diaz Pinto of 49 YEARS - NATURAL SON OF Jesus Diaz AND OF WITH Alejandra Portillo , OF 28 , YEARS NATURAL DAUGHTER OF Santos Portillo AND . GODPARENTS AND WITNESSES MESSRS. Tulio Chinchilla and Rosa de Chinchilla SIGNED BY: Rev. P. Eduardo Rodriguez AND FOR IT TO BE ON RECORD, HAS SIGNED ANS SEALED IN San Pedro Sula ON THE 20th DAY OF THE MONTH OF August 19 91 REV. SIGNATURE AND SEAL Translated by Linda Matta. I am fluent bilingual (Spanish / English). To the best of my knowledge this document is accurate in its and its Spanish original copy. Signature: translation Linda Matta equal to the Date: 12/10/91 STATE OF CALIFORNIA COUNTY of Los Angeles subscribed and SWORN before me on this 13TH., DAY OF December OF 1991. EQuia Receively OFFICIAL SEAL ELVIA BENITEZ NOTARY PUBLIC - CALIFORNIA LOS ANGELES COUNTY My comm. expires AUG 24, 1993
